**Soups**

* **Asian:**
    * Hot and Sour Soup (Chinese)
    * Tom Yum Soup (Thai)
    * Miso Soup (Japanese)
    * Pho (Vietnamese)
    * Ramen (Japanese)
* **Mediterranean:**
    * Gazpacho (Spanish)
    * Lentil Soup (Turkish)
    * Bouillabaisse (French)
    * Avgolemono (Greek)
    * Ribollita (Italian)

**Stews**

* **Asian:**
    * Japanese Curry (Japanese)
    * Massaman Curry (Thai)
    * Sukiyaki (Japanese)
    * Samgyeopsal Stew (Korean)
    * Pho Bo (Vietnamese)
* **Mediterranean:**
    * Cassoulet (French)
    * Paella (Spanish)
    * Bobotie (South African)
    * Moules-frites (Belgian)
    * Tagine (Moroccan)

**Hot Drinks**

* **Asian:**
    * Green Tea (China, Japan)
    * Matcha (Japan)
    * Oolong Tea (Taiwan)
    * Pu-erh Tea (China)
    * Ginger Tea (Various Asian countries)
* **Mediterranean:**
    * Turkish Coffee (Turkey)
    * Moroccan Mint Tea (Morocco)
    * Salep (Turkey)
    * Sahlep (Lebanon)
    * Horchata (Spain)
